  <div class="chat-interface">
    <div class="chat-header">
      <h1>Chat with your files</h1>
      <p>Unleash the power of conversation with Zone! Our innovative AI transforms complex documents into lively, interactive chats. Dive into a world where vital information is just a question away, making discovery seamless and enjoyable for everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="chat-features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h2>Effortless Information Navigation</h2>
        <p>Our AI doesn't just search; it understands. Get accurate, context-aware answers to complex queries without manual digging through hundreds of pages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h2>Instant Knowledge Retrieval</h2>
        <p>Instantly access the data you need through Zone's quick-query technology. It's like having a personal assistant for every document.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
