        <p>Transform your document review process with interactive dialogues. Zone turns monotonous scrolling into engaging conversations with your files.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gradient-section">
      <div class="chat-section-left">
        <h1 class="start-chatting-title">Start Chatting</h1>
        <p class="chat-description">Revolutionize document management with our AI-powered chat. Experience tailored dialogues, insightful summaries, and unmatched clarity for all your complex content.</p>
        <button class="start-chat-btn">Zone in</button>
      </div>
      <div class="phone-chat-box">
        <div class="chat-window">
          <!-- Mockup Chat Messages -->
          <div class="chat-message bot-message">
            <div class="profile-icon">A</div>
            <span class="message-content">What is my action item for tomorrow's product meeting, as discussed during yesterday's team sync?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-message user-message">
            <div class="profile-icon">B</div>
            <span class="message-content">According to the meeting transcript, you are expected to bring a preliminary audit of your two direct competitors: Acme studio and Coss.</span>
          </div>
          <!-- More messages here -->
        </div>
        <div class="chat-input-bar">
          <input type="text" class="chat-input-field" placeholder="Type a message...">
